{
  "total_duration": 667.079,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 10.224,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的题目是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Shopping made easy"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，中文可以说“购物变得很方便”。但这不是购物技巧课，而是一个 irony，反讽标题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 10.574,
      "end": 19.054,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正常意思是：shopping becomes easier。故事里的意思却是：一个女人让 shopping 变 easy，是因为她根本没有付钱。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 19.404,
      "end": 28.884,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以先把 moral frame 放清楚：walk out of a shop without paying 是偷东西，是不诚实，也是不合法的。课文不是在夸她聪明。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 29.233,
      "end": 39.661,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detective"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是拿放大镜破案的 Sherlock Holmes，而更像商场里的 store detective，防损员，安保观察员。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 40.011,
      "end": 50.907,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "assistant"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里是 shop assistant，售货员，店员；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "articles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是商店里的小商品，不是报纸杂志里的文章。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 51.257,
      "end": 64.525,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "开头"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "People are not so honest as they once were"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，听起来像老派抱怨。我们不要理解成“现代人都不诚实”，只把它当作主人公引出这件 shoplifting story 的方式。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 64.874,
      "end": 81.666,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的记忆链是：detective watches, woman enters, small articles, expensive dress, assistant wraps it, woman leaves without paying, arrested, assistant is daughter, and the word"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'gave'"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "has quotation marks."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 82.016,
      "end": 89.736,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一幅画，是一个大型商店的星期一上午。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A detective recently watched a well-dressed woman."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 90.086,
      "end": 100.402,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "well-dressed"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是穿着讲究。这个细节会制造反差：她看起来像普通顾客，甚至很体面，但 detective 已经在观察她。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 100.752,
      "end": 111.416,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她不是偶然来一次。课文说她"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "always went into a large store on Monday mornings"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。always 和 Monday mornings 说明这是 repeated pattern。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 111.766,
      "end": 121.213,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一天店里人少："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "There were fewer people in the shop than usual."
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fewer"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是更少，修饰可数的人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 121.563,
      "end": 131.987,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "人少就带出下一句比较："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It was easier for the detective to watch her."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "fewer people makes watching easier。比较结构在帮故事往前走。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 132.337,
      "end": 140.201,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二幅画，看起来还是 normal shopping。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The woman first bought a few small articles."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 140.551,
      "end": 149.943,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "articles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里就是 items for sale，小商品，小物件。她先买这些，是为了让自己看起来像普通顾客。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 150.292,
      "end": 156.684,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "过了一会儿，动作变大了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She chose one of the most expensive dresses in the shop."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 157.034,
      "end": 165.426,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "one of the most expensive dresses"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“最贵的裙子之一”。small articles 和 expensive dress 形成清楚对比。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 165.776,
      "end": 173.936,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "画面里要记住 store path：entrance, small goods, dress rack。现在她已经从小商品走到了贵裙子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 174.286,
      "end": 182.658,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三幅画，关键人物出现："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "She handed it to an assistant."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的 assistant 是店员，不是办公室助理。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 183.008,
      "end": 188.976,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "店员动作非常快："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The assistant wrapped it up for her as quickly as possible."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 189.325,
      "end": 198.309,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "wrap up"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是把东西包起来；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as quickly as possible"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是尽可能快。这个速度让事情显得不太正常。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 198.659,
      "end": 205.171,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后最关键的一句来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The woman simply took the parcel and walked out of the shop without paying."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 205.521,
      "end": 218.289,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "parcel"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是包好的包裹；"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "without paying"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是没有付钱。不是忘记拿 receipt，不是 discount，也不是 free gift。她拿着商店的东西走了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 218.638,
      "end": 227.342,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四幅画是 reveal。课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she was arrested, the detective found out that the shop assistant was her daughter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 227.692,
      "end": 237.428,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "was arrested"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是被逮捕，被带走处理。我们不需要把画面做成警匪片，重点是 the truth was discovered。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 237.778,
      "end": 242.738,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "真相是：那个飞快包裙子的 shop assistant，是这个女人的 daughter。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 243.088,
      "end": 249.032,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一行有反讽："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The girl 'gave' her mother a free dress once a week!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 249.382,
      "end": 260.174,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'gave'"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "要加引号？因为这不是一个真正的 gift。商店的裙子不是女儿自己的东西，她不能把它送给妈妈。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 260.523,
      "end": 267.843,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以标题的反转是：shopping was made easy only because someone inside helped break the rule。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 268.193,
      "end": 271.553,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我们来把这课最容易误会的地方拆开。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 271.903,
      "end": 277.388,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "题目说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Shopping made easy"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，是不是说买东西很方便？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 277.738,
      "end": 287.298,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "字面上是。但故事里是 irony。她让购物“方便”的方法，是不付钱就离开。所以这不是 tip，是 warning。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 287.648,
      "end": 292.64,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "detective"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是不是侦探小说里的侦探？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 292.99,
      "end": 299.79,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这课更像 store detective，商场防损员。他在大商店里观察有没有人偷拿商品。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 300.14,
      "end": 303.938,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "assistant"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是店员，对吗？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 304.288,
      "end": 313.448,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。shop assistant 可以帮顾客拿衣服、包东西、指路，也可能收款。但她不能把商店的东西随便送给亲人。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 313.798,
      "end": 317.795,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "article"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我以前以为是文章。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 318.145,
      "end": 329.273,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很好，这里要换意思。在 shop 里，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "articles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是 items，商品。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a few small articles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是几样小商品。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 329.622,
      "end": 334.194,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那最后的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'gave'"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么有引号？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 334.544,
      "end": 343.384,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为主人公在提醒我们：这个 gave 不是真的 gave。A real gift is given by the owner. A shop assistant cannot give away the store's dress."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 343.734,
      "end": 355.774,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "背诵时别把它背成犯罪方法，要背成 observation chain：detective notices a repeated pattern, follows the shopping path, and discovers the hidden family arrangement."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 356.124,
      "end": 359.388,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "People are not so honest as they once were."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 359.737,
      "end": 364.489,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The temptation to steal is greater than ever before -- especially in large shops."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 364.839,
      "end": 370.791,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A detective recently watched a well-dressed woman who always went into a large store on Monday mornings."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 371.141,
      "end": 378.365,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "One Monday, there were fewer people in the shop than usual when the woman came in, so it was easier for the detective to watch her."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 378.715,
      "end": 382.123,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The woman first bought a few small articles."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 382.473,
      "end": 390.729,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "After a little time, she chose one of the most expensive dresses in the shop and handed it to an assistant who wrapped it up for her as quickly as possible."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 391.079,
      "end": 395.591,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Then the woman simply took the parcel and walked out of the shop without paying."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 395.941,
      "end": 401.029,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she was arrested, the detective found out that the shop assistant was her daughter."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 401.379,
      "end": 405.099,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The girl 'gave' her mother a free dress once a week!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 405.448,
      "end": 408.328,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "temptation"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "temptation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 408.678,
      "end": 410.55,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "temptation"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "temptation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 410.9,
      "end": 424.86,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "temptation"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "temptation"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是诱惑，尤其是想做一件不对、或者不明智的事的冲动。比如 temptation to steal, temptation to cheat, temptation to eat candy before dinner。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 425.21,
      "end": 437.326,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "temptation"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The temptation to steal is greater than ever before."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "主人公用这个词引出大商店里偷东西的风险，但我们不把它讲成“大家都这样”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 437.676,
      "end": 440.308,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "article"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "article"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 440.657,
      "end": 442.313,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "article"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "article"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 442.663,
      "end": 454.967,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "article"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "article"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最常见的意思可以是文章，但这课不是。这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "articles"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是商店里的物品，商品，items for sale。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 455.317,
      "end": 463.281,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "article"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The woman first bought a few small articles."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "她先买几样小东西，让自己看起来像 normal shopper。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 463.631,
      "end": 466.431,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "arrest"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "arrest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 466.78,
      "end": 468.388,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "arrest"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "arrest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 468.738,
      "end": 477.482,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "arrest"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "arrest"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是逮捕，或者因为可能违法而被带走处理。课文用的是被动："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she was arrested"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 477.832,
      "end": 489.756,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "arrest"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she was arrested, the detective found out the truth."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意我们不强调吓人的画面，只强调 consequence：rule-breaking was discovered。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 490.106,
      "end": 493.666,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的 grammar 用一架 comparison ladder 串起来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 494.016,
      "end": 504.415,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "not so honest as they once were"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这是把主人公眼里的现在和过去作比较，意思是“不像以前那样诚实”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 504.765,
      "end": 512.581,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "greater than ever before"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这里 greater than 表示偷东西的诱惑比以前更大。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 512.931,
      "end": 522.291,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fewer people in the shop than usual"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "fewer"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "修饰 people，因为 people 可以数。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 522.641,
      "end": 531.024,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "easier for the detective to watch her"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。人更少，所以更容易观察她。cause and effect 很清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 531.374,
      "end": 540.406,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第五格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "one of the most expensive dresses"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。one of the most 表示“最……之一”，不是随便一件普通裙子。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 540.756,
      "end": 549.564,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第六格："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "as quickly as possible"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。as quickly as possible 就是 as fast as she can，尽可能快。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 549.914,
      "end": 558.138,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有一个被动："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When she was arrested"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。句子重点放在“她发生了什么”，不是把 arrest 的人放在前面。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 558.487,
      "end": 570.319,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后一块是 punctuation with meaning："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "'gave'"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的引号告诉我们，这个词不能按真实礼物理解。It was not a gift. It was theft helped from inside the store."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 570.669,
      "end": 579.349,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现在把这课放进今天的购物场景。你和朋友在一家大商店里，朋友说：“直接拿走吧，反正没人发现。”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 579.699,
      "end": 587.859,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "你要练三件事：refuse the dishonest suggestion, explain the rule, and guide the person to the checkout。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 588.209,
      "end": 592.065,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "We can't take it without paying."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 592.415,
      "end": 599.295,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再说清楚："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It is not a free gift."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "A real free gift must come from the store or the owner."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 599.644,
      "end": 603.556,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后给行动："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Let's go to the checkout first."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 603.906,
      "end": 610.29,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "如果想说完整一点，可以用这一句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The shop owns it, so we must pay for it first."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 610.64,
      "end": 618.6,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这题的重点不是吓人，而是把 trust 说清楚：shopping works because people pay before they leave."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 618.95,
      "end": 644.457,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "outro",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
